    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Campaign for co-Chair of the Council for Science and Technology
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A campaign has launched to select a new co-Chair for the Prime Minister’s Council for Science and Technology.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
